snippet.title: Predator: Hunting Grounds Official Trailer | Now on PS5 and Xbox Series X|S
snippet.description:
Play with friends in this 4v1 asymmetrical shooter as part of a highly trained Fireteam tasked with completing paramilitary missions or as the lone Predator hunting your prey.

Predator: Hunting Grounds is now on PS5 and Xbox Series X|S for the first time! New Predators to follow!

The physical PS5 edition launches December 6th, with preorders coming soon.

Prepare for the hunt and get Predator: Hunting Grounds!

Join our community and follow our socials!
